regexFilenameFromData.code:
function regexFilenameFromData(filename, outputFormat) {
    if(!filename) return
    regex = /^.*\./ //regex everything before dot (inculding dot)
    newName = filename.match(regex)
    newName = newName.toString() + outputFormat //adding a new file extension
    
    return newName
}
